Definition: in a set manner without serious attention
Example: as a formality; they answered my letter pro forma; he kissed her cheek perfunctorily
Synonyms: adj, all, careless, perfunctory, pro_forma, in, a, set, manner, without, serious, attention, as, formality, they, answered, my, letter, pro, forma, he, kissed, her, cheek
Category: adv.all
